                               በቅድመ፡ 
                                 <sic>ነገድያን፡</sic>
                               በሐረተ፡ ዝዌላ፡ ዘተናገሮ፡ አው፡ ዘከሰሶ፡ አው፡ ዘተዐደዎ፡ ውጉዘ፡ 
                              ለይኩን፡ በአፈ፡ 
                                 <sic>፲ው፭፡</sic>
                               
                              <add place="inline">
                                 <supplied reason="omitted">ነቢያት፡</supplied>
                              </add> ወበአፈ፡ ፲ወ፪፡ 
                              ሐዋርያት፡ ወበአፉሃ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወበአፈ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ለይኩን፡ ለዓለም፡ አሜን።</q>
                           <note>The note states that the book was purchased by <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11369MekhaMa">Mǝkḥa Māryām</persName> from 
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11370Samuel">
                                 <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName> Sāmuʾel</persName> for 60 <foreign>madin</foreign> in <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3790HaratZ">Harata Zǝwelā</placeName>. 
                           The note conclude with an excommunication against those who erase or steal the book.</note>
                        </item>
                      
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#307ra" facs="0309"/>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ዛቲ፡ 
                                 <sic>መጽሐፍ።</sic>
                               ዘምክሃ፡ ማርያም፡ ወልደ፡ አቡነ፡ ኤዎስጣቴዎስ፡ ደብረ፡ ማርያም፡</q>
                           <note>The note states that the book belongs to <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11369MekhaMa">Mǝkḥa Māryām</persName>, 
                              <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11207Ewostateans">spiritual son of ʾEwosṭātewos</persName> of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2317DabraM">Dabra Māryām</placeName>.
                           </note>
                        </item>
                    
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>The shelfmark of the Vatican Library <q xml:lang="la">Vat. | 38 | Aethiop.</q> is written on the cover, together with the coat of arms of 
                              pope <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7893PiusIX">Pius IX</persName>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <locus target="#Ir" facs="0002"/>
                           <desc>The title of the book <q xml:lang="la">euang<supplied reason="explanation">elium</supplied> s Marci s. Iohannis f. 167</q> and the
                               shelfmark of the Vatican Library <q>38</q> are written in a <date>18th-century</date> hand. 
                           </desc>
                        </item>
